            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-42b8fef4-5e5c-4efe-8f65-dad6fd9bbee4">
                Mr. Maxton  (Glasgow, Bridgeton)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-42b8fef4-5e5c-4efe-8f65-dad6fd9bbee4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
