    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I do not think I can discuss all the treaties—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6a46e02f-5555-4cdf-8602-efa9bcb45d5e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
