<p class="">What category does the Brains Trust come under?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-813dd0ae-dc53-4ad8-bd95-12ea04c2b06a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
