<p class="">So do we.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5ec4d79f-0750-42e4-bbcc-b28fda40065a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1942-02-24/debates/02bca043-5cc0-400a-89de-d5c5f276194d/MinisterialChanges#contribution-5ec4d79f-0750-42e4-bbcc-b28fda40065a">
