<p class="">Has the hon. Gentleman ever heard of the text, "Resist the evil"?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a29b0b1a-3153-4ddd-94e5-1aa4f930ef94" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
