<p class="">I apologise, Sir. I was not aware that quotations from speeches in another place were not allowed. Perhaps I may paraphrase what he said.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a711068e-12c5-42da-bace-73bfd00d6a20" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
